These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, san-francisco, london, prague
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| City   | boston | prague | san-francisco | london |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, russian, french, german
1. the spanish is on the left of the german##1
2. the russian is in an odd position##4
3. the russian is on the left or right of the spanish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality   | russian | spanish | german | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
