1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
2. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to berlin is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to liverpool##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| City   | hannover | venice | berlin | liverpool |

