.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, prince, chaman, swisher
1. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
3. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | chaman | fonseca | swisher | prince |

 #################################

 
