.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, march, september, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Birthday   | december | march | june | september |

