.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, fishing, hiking, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | hiking | traveling | fishing | photography |

